    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UnITED\nCHICAGO\nDecember 13, 1979\nOur Friendly Times\nUnited's Sunbirds are coming\nDecember 13! 15 nonstops a day to\nMiami, Ft. Lauderdale, Tampa/St.\nPete, Orlando/Walt Disney World,\nSarasota, Ft. Myers \u0026 West Palm\nBeach!\nThere's no place like Florida. And\nthere's no better way to get there\nthan United's famous Sunbird\nService. We'll warm you up on your\nway to the sun with a complimentary\nSunbird Swizzle and a tempting meal.\nAnd even though our Sunbirds won't\nmigrate until Dec. 13, you can book\nspace to your favorite Florida sunspot\ntoday. Call your Travel Agent today.\nOr call United at 569-3000.\nComplete schedules inside."
